name: Dressing the teddy bears
description:
This photo was taken in Paris in November 2018. A man dresses teddy bears in costume during the preparations of the Christmas windows of a store.

This photo is part of my Streetphotography series "The Street Session vol.2018" visible on my website at: https://samuelboivin.fr/the-street-session-vol-2018/

Samuel Boivin
